data.description: PRICE IMPROVEMENT!  Come see this exquisite modern home, nestled in the quiet and desirable neighborhood of the SW Cape.  This 4 bedroom, 2 bath home is situated along a freshwater canal with Western exposure.  The main suite features a tray ceiling, two walk-in closets and a large master soaking tub and walk in shower.  The kitchen overlooks the family room and eat-in dining area. There is also a separate formal dining for entertaining. Plenty of closet space and shelving, granite counter tops, paver pool deck & lanai. The large enclosed lanai has plenty of space for entertaining and enjoying your heated pool and stunning sunsets.  This home is situated in one of the best locations in Cape Coral, you're close to community hot spots, dining and shopping. This home could be a great Air BNB.   A Wind Mitigation is on hand.
